snippet.title: Creeping It Reel - Nintendo - Mega Cat Studios
snippet.description:
Get Spooky with some creepy chiptunes from Mitch Foster & Danimal Cannon while you practice dance moves from the Dancing Pumpkin Man, trick or treat in true 8 bit glory.

Get your copy at: https://megacatstudios.com/collections/nes-games/products/creeping-it-reel

Come join in on the discussion at our official Discord: https://discordapp.com/invite/megacat

Creeping it Reel is not licensed, sponsored, published, or endorsed by Nintendo Co. Ltd, or their affiliates.

Mega Cat Studios is an independent games development studio. This title is an unofficial and unlicensed release for the Nintendo console, and is not affiliated with Nintendo Co., Ltd, or their affiliates.
